            . I am a pawnbroker in Petty France; the prisoner brought a silver spoon the 11th of May to pledge for 7 s. I took it in; I know it is one of these spoons; I cannot say which because they are mixed.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I never saw the spoons till I saw them before the Justice, nor none of these people.</p>
